---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Getting Started">
  <div class="content">
    <h1>Getting Started</h1>
    
    <section class="section">
      <h2>Prerequisites</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/azure/developer/azure-developer-cli/install-azd">Azure Developer CLI (azd)</a></li>
        <li>GitHub Copilot subscription (optional, for AI features)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Installation</h2>
      <p>Install the extension using the Azure Developer CLI:</p>
      <pre><code>azd extension install jongio.azd.copilot</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Verify Installation</h2>
      <p>Check that the extension is installed correctly:</p>
      <pre><code>azd copilot version</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Usage</h2>
      <p>Once installed, you can use the extension with:</p>
      <pre><code>azd copilot --help</code></pre>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Next Steps</h2>
      <p>
        Check out the <a href="https://github.com/jongio/azd-copilot">GitHub repository</a> 
        for more documentation and examples.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .content {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
  }

  .section ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .section li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section pre {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
